Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.08,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道被誤解的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.75,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,(Missiles flying, children getting shot)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.75,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,（導彈凌空，孩童中彈）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.65,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Swindles everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.65,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:33.40,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,People who should be the most loves ones, killing each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:33.40,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,原本至愛之人 如今互相屠戮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:40.20,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you keep an eye off, things get stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:40.20,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,一時鬆懈 萬物盡失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.42,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The world Is like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.42,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.45,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The world we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.45,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.69,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The unknown world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.69,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.11,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our hands Covering it up, acting like you don't see a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.11,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,超出了我們的掌控 掩藏它吧，如同你從未目睹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.25,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think it's a different thing You won't notice that the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.25,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,若你認為這只是不同的事情 你將不會發現 你所在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.76,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,you live in is eventually hitting towards this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.76,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,最終也會迎來這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:03.50,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it Oh yeah ! The world is all linked together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:03.50,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,看著它！Oh Yeah！這世界已被鏈在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.46,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Save (hey!) our loved (hey!) ones and the world (because breaking)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.46,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救所愛和這世界 （因為）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.11,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,(Down the pile wood castle is easy) The peaceful days lasting is a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.11,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,（碾平圓木堆堡壘並非難事）持久的和平只是願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.66,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.66,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:17.14,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,How many.. tickets "to live today" are.. (Left!!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:17.14,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩多少「今日生還」的（入場券！）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.83,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at the time you were! playing cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.83,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你打撲克的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.58,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in the world.. somebody is crying.. ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.58,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界某處也有人正在號哭……Ah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於公園內出現大量死屍一事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有幾個問題需要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙手抱頭蹲下！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明把礙事的跟班殺乾淨了重獲自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好不容易這幫人自己聚集起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連著康復運動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 風感覺都聚攏到她的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反物質 你們沒見過吧
